reviewText: I wasn't really happy that it was from a public library.

Loved this movie. It's one of those sweet feel good movies that leaves you with a sense of satisfaction at the end. Robert De Niro is excellent. And Anne Hathaway is her normal quirky self torn between being serious and anal and uncertain. Great movie for the family.
Teresa J. Reasor
Too many stops and missed content each time.  Could not enjoy it.  Ferne
